data.title: Family of Nikolas Cassadine & Emily Quartermaine
meta_keywords: family of Nikolas Cassadine & Emily Quartermaine
data.meta_description: Family of Nikolas Cassadine & Emily Quartermaine.
data.text:
Nikolas Cassadine

Nikolas, known as Nik, was born on November 6th, 1981 in Athens, Greece.

Emily Quartermaine

Emily was born on January 15th, 1984 in Phoenix, Arizona. She died due to murder / assassination, strangled to death by Diego Alcazar, at the age of 23 on November 14th, 2007 at Wyndemere Castle. The funeral took place on November 28th, 2007 at the Queen of Angels Cathedral. Her body was entombed on November 28th, 2007 in the Quartermaine Crypt.
